data-src="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-how-to-start-a-business-in-the-virgin-islands-complete-800x800-20210111.jpeg?crop=1:1,smart&width=250&dpr=2" class="lazyload" width="250" height="250" alt="How to Start a Business in the Virgin Islands:">
</picture></div><p>In the U.S. Virgin Islands, most businesses must be registered with the Lieutenant Governor’s Office Division of Corporations and Trademarks. All businesses must obtain a business license and register with the local Bureau of Internal Revenue (BIR), as taxes must be paid to the BIR instead of the IRS.</p></div><div
id="how-to-start-a-business-in-the-virgin-islands-section1" class="how-to-section"><div
class="section-title">
<span>1.&nbsp;</span><h3 id=form-your-business>Form your business.</h3></div><div
id="how-to-start-a-business-in-the-virgin-islands-section1-step1" class="step"><div
class="step-desc"><div
class="step-title">
<span>1.1&nbsp;</span><h4 id=review-formation-options-in-the-u-s-virgin-islands>Review formation options in the U.S. Virgin Islands.</h4></div><div
class="image-wrapper"><div
class="image-holder">
<img
data-src="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-familiarize-yourself-with-the-key-business-structures-288x288-20200820_2023-09-15-072444_xekq.png?crop=1:1,smart&width=144&dpr=2" class="lazyload" width="144" height="144" alt="Review formation options in the U.S. Virgin Islands."></div></div><p>The U.S. Virgin Islands offer <a
href="#virgin-islands-business-types">seven ways of forming your business</a>, which we cover in detail below. Review these closely and pick the one that fits your business best.</p></div></div><div
id="how-to-start-a-business-in-the-virgin-islands-section1-step2" class="step"><div
class="step-desc"><div
class="step-title">
<span>1.2&nbsp;</span><h4 id=name-your-business>Name your business.</h4></div><div
class="image-wrapper"><div
class="image-holder">
<img
data-src="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-name-your-business-288x288-2020092.jpeg?crop=1:1,smart&width=144&dpr=2" class="lazyload" width="144" height="144" alt="Name your business."></div></div><p>Once you have decided on a business name, you must <a
href="https://www.namesnack.com/guides/virgin-islands-business-search">check its availability</a>. If your preferred business name is available, you can go ahead and reserve or register your business name using the online filing system, Catalyst. You will have to create an account to access the online services.</p><div
class="step-direction tip">
