class="col-12 faq-item"><h3 id=how-much-is-a-business-license-in-the-virgin-islands class="question">How much is a business license in the Virgin Islands?</h3><div
class="answer"><p>The cost of a business license in the Virgin Islands depends on the type of business you are starting.</p></div></div><div
class="col-12 faq-item"><h3 id=how-do-i-set-up-a-company-in-the-virgin-islands class="question">How do I set up a company in the Virgin Islands?</h3><div
class="answer"><ol><li><a
href="#form-your-business">Form your business</a>.</li><li><a
href="#get-an-employer-identification-number">Apply for your employer identification number</a>.</li><li><a
href="#register-your-business-in-the-u-s-virgin-islands">Register your business</a>.</li><li><a
href="#obtain-necessary-permits-and-certifications">Obtain the necessary permits and licenses</a>.</li><li><a
